div.p: Go module paths Container name mapping

Legend Purple = shared packages (imported by all services via replace directive) Blue = url-service (container: url-service, port 8081) Green = analytics-service (container: analytics-service, port 8082) Orange = user-service (container: user-service, port 8083) Pink = notification-service (container: notification-service, port 8084) Indigo = gateway (container: gateway, port 8080) Dark boxes = Docker container identity + network bindings
go.mod module github.com/yourhandle/ url-shortener/shared go 1.23 dep: zerolog v1.33.0
go.mod module github.com/yourhandle/ url-shortener/gateway go 1.23 replace shared ../shared
main.go ConnectRedis (rate limits) NewJWTVerifier NewCircuitBreaker NewReverseProxy (4 targets) Startup health checks Middleware: Correlation RequestLogger GatewayJWT RateLimit CircuitBreaker
Dockerfile FROM golang:1.23-alpine AS builder FROM alpine:3.20 EXPOSE 8080
packages/ circuitbreaker/ ratelimit/ proxy/ middleware/ handler/ router/
container: gateway port: 8080 8080 Redis: redis:6379 (rate limits) JWT_SECRET (verify only) Routes all /api/* + /r/{code}
events.go package events DomainEvent interface URLCreatedEvent URLClickedEvent URLDeletedEvent MilestoneReachedEvent EventType constants
logger.go package logger New(serviceName, w) zerolog.Logger WithCorrelationID(log, id) RequestLogger(log) middleware
types.go package auth JWTVerifier interface Claims struct Sentinel errors
jwt_middleware.go package middleware RequireAuth(verifier, log) ClaimsFromContext(ctx)
go.mod module github.com/yourhandle/ url-shortener/url-service go 1.23 replace shared ../../shared
main.go ConnectDB ConnectRedis ConnectRabbitMQ OutboxPoller.Start() Routes: GET /{code} POST /shorten GET /urls DELETE /urls/{code} GET /health
Dockerfile FROM golang:1.23-alpine AS builder FROM alpine:3.20 EXPOSE 8081
packages/ codegen/ repository/ cache/ amqp/ outbox/ service/ handler/ migrations/
container: url-service port: 8081 8081 DB: url_db:5432 Redis: redis:6379 MQ: rabbitmq:5672
go.mod module github.com/yourhandle/ url-shortener/analytics-service go 1.23 replace shared ../../shared
main.go ConnectDB ConnectRabbitMQ ClickProcessor consumer Routes: GET /stats/{code} GET /stats/{code}/timeline GET /health
Dockerfile FROM golang:1.23-alpine AS builder FROM alpine:3.20 EXPOSE 8082
packages/ repository/ consumer/ milestone/ publisher/ handler/ migrations/
container: analytics-service port: 8082 8082 DB: analytics_db:5432 MQ: rabbitmq:5672 queue: analytics.clicks
go.mod module github.com/yourhandle/ url-shortener/user-service go 1.23 replace shared ../../shared
main.go ConnectDB ConnectRabbitMQ Routes: POST /register POST /login GET /me (auth) GET /health
Dockerfile FROM golang:1.23-alpine AS builder FROM alpine:3.20 EXPOSE 8083
packages/ repository/ auth/ service/ handler/ migrations/
container: user-service port: 8083 8083 DB: user_db:5432 MQ: rabbitmq:5672 JWT_SECRET (issues + verifies)

packages/ repository/ consumer/ handler/ migrations/
